snippet.title: Traffic Cop for Atari 2600 Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer for Traffic Cop on the Atari 2600.

For more information on this and other games by Blue Tail Games head over here: http://bluetailgames.weebly.com/

Blue Tail Games is the spiritual successor or rebranding if you will from rhillfakestudios, founded by the same person.
